  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you are the target of an attack, you may perform a reposition combat maneuver against an impaled creature as an immediate action without provoking an attack of opportunity. You may reposition the impaled enemy into occupied squares other than your own, but they are shunted to the nearest unoccupied square after the attack resolves. If the impaled creature&#8217;s new position would place them in the path of the attack targeting you, the attack is instead rolled against them.</p>\n",
